 .) Manage Jenkins > Configure System 
   - Maven Configuration > Default global settings provider > Global settings file on filesystem
     .) File path: /opt/maven_config/.m2/settings.xml
   - Maven > Maven installations > Add Maven
     .) Deselect 'Install automatically', 
     .) Name: maven3
     .) MAVEN_HOME: /opt/apache-maven-3.3.3


===== Continuous Delivery Demo bookstore =====

-) SCRIPTING

 .) demo/createJob.sh

-) MANUAL

.) Create new job
 .) Project name: bookstore
 .) Maven project
 .) Source Code Management
  .) Git: https://github.com/tecris/bookstore.git


.) Build
  .) Goals and options: clean deploy
.) Post Build:
  .) Execute Shell: 
    .) Build image with each build using following command:
    .) curl -v -X POST -H "Content-Type:application/tar" --data-binary '@/opt/docker/dockerfiles/Dockerfile.bookstore.tar.gz' \
	http://192.168.1.69:4243/build?t=org.tecris:5000/bookstore:${BUILD_NUMBER}
